\c 10
\s Inhlupheko yesificaminwembili: Isikhonyane
\p
\v 1 IN\nd kosi\nd* yasisithi kuMozisi: Yana kuFaro, ngoba mina ngenze inhliziyo yakhe yaba nzima\x + 4.21; 7.3; 8.15; 9.12.\x* lenhliziyo yenceku zakhe, ukuze ngenze lezizibonakaliso zami phambi kwakhe\f + \fk phambi kwakhe: \fl Heb. \fqa phakathi kwakhe.\f*,
\v 2 lokuthi ulandise endlebeni zendodana yakho lendodana yendodana yakho\x + Jow. 1.3. Dute. 4.9. Hlab. 78.5.\x* ukuthi ngenze kabuhlungu kumaGibhithe\x + 1 Sam. 6.6.\x* lezibonakaliso zami engizenze phakathi kwawo, ukuze lazi ukuthi ngiyiN\nd kosi\nd*.
\v 3 UMozisi loAroni basebesiya kuFaro, bathi kuye: Itsho njalo iN\nd kosi\nd*, uNkulunkulu wamaHebheru, \add ithi\add*: Koze kube nini usala ukuzithoba phambi kwami? Yekela isizwe sami sihambe, bangikhonze.
\v 4 Ngoba uba usala ukuyekela isizwe sami sihambe, khangela, kusasa ngizaletha isikhonyane emngceleni wakho\x + Levi 11.22. Zaga 30.27. Jow. 1.4; 2.25. Isam. 9.3.\x*,
\v 5 njalo sizasibekela ubuso bomhlaba ukuze ungawuboni umhlaba, sizakudla insalela yokwaphephayo, okwalisalelayo esiqhothweni, sidle sonke isihlahla esikhulela wena ensimini\x + 9.32.\x*.
\v 6 Sizagcwalisa izindlu zakho lezindlu zezinceku zakho zonke lezindlu zawo wonke amaGibhithe\x + 8.21.\x*, oyihlo abangazanga basibone laboyise baboyihlo, kusukela ngosuku ababakhona emhlabeni kuze kube lamuhla. Wasetshibilika, waphuma kuFaro.
\v 7 Lenceku zikaFaro zathi kuye: Koze kube nini lo esiba ngumjibila kithi\x + 23.33; 34.12. Josh. 23.13. 1 Sam. 18.21. 1 Kor. 7.35.\x*? Yekela amadoda ahambe, akhonze iN\nd kosi\nd* uNkulunkulu wawo; kawukazi yini ukuthi iGibhithe isichithekile?
\v 8 UMozisi loAroni babuyiselwa kuFaro; wasesithi kubo: Hambani likhonze iN\nd kosi\nd* uNkulunkulu wenu. Ngobani kanye labo abazahamba?
\v 9 UMozisi wasesithi: Sizahamba labatsha bethu labadala bethu, lamadodana ethu lamadodakazi ethu, lezimvu zethu lenkomo zethu sizahamba, ngoba silomkhosi weN\nd kosi\nd*.
\v 10 Wasesithi kubo: IN\nd kosi\nd* ibe lani ngokunjalo\x + 5.1.\x*, njengoba ngizaliyekela lihambe labantwanyana benu! Bonani ngoba kulokubi phambi kwenu.
\v 11 Kungabi njalo! Hambani khathesi, madoda, liyikhonze iN\nd kosi\nd*, ngoba yikho elikudingayo. Basebebaxotsha ebusweni bukaFaro.
\p
\v 12 IN\nd kosi\nd* yasisithi kuMozisi: Yelula isandla sakho phezu kwelizwe leGibhithe\x + 7.19; 9.22; 10.21.\x*, ngenxa yesikhonyane, ukuze senyukele phezu kwelizwe leGibhithe, sidle wonke umbhida welizwe lakho konke isiqhotho esikutshiyileyo\x + 10.4,5.\x*.
\v 13 UMozisi waseyelula intonga yakhe phezu kwelizwe leGibhithe; iN\nd kosi\nd* yasiqhuba umoya wempumalanga elizweni, lonke lolosuku lobusuku bonke; kwasekusithi ekuseni, umoya wempumalanga wenyusa isikhonyane.
\v 14 Isikhonyane sasesisenyukela phezu kwelizwe lonke leGibhithe\x + Hlab. 78.46; 105.34.\x*, sehlela emngceleni wonke weGibhithe, esinzima kakhulu. Phambi kwaso akuzange kube khona isikhonyane esinjalo njengaso, futhi kakuyikuba khona esinjalo emva kwaso\x + Jow. 2.2.\x*.
\v 15 Ngoba sasibekela ubuso belizwe lonke, kwaze kwafiphazwa ilizwe; sadla wonke umbhida welizwe laso sonke isithelo sezihlahla isiqhotho esasitshiyayo\x + Hlab. 105.35.\x*; kakusalanga lutho oluluhlaza esihlahleni, lombhida weganga, elizweni lonke leGibhithe.
\p
\v 16 UFaro wasephangisa ukubabiza oMozisi loAroni, wathi: Ngonile eN\nd kosi\nd*ni uNkulunkulu wenu lakini\x + 9.27.\x*.
\v 17 Khathesi-ke ake lithethelele isono sami okwalesisikhathi kuphela, liyincenge iN\nd kosi\nd*\x + 9.28.\x* uNkulunkulu wenu ukuthi isuse kimi lokhu ukufa kuphela.
\v 18 Wasephuma kuFaro, wayincenga iN\nd kosi\nd*\x + 8.30; 9.33.\x*.
\v 19 IN\nd kosi\nd* yasiphendula umoya wentshonalanga olamandla kakhulu owenyusa isikhonyane, wasiphosela oLwandle oluBomvu\x + Jow. 2.20.\x*; kakusalanga sikhonyane lesisodwa kuwo wonke umngcele weGibhithe.
\v 20 Kodwa iN\nd kosi\nd* yayenza lukhuni inhliziyo kaFaro\x + 4.21; 9.12; 10.27; 11.10; 14.4,8.\x*, kazabayekela abantwana bakoIsrayeli bahambe.
\s Inhlupheko yesificamunwemunye: Umnyama ophumputhekayo
\p
\v 21 IN\nd kosi\nd* yasisithi kuMozisi: Yelulela isandla sakho emazulwini\x + 10.12.\x*, ukuze kube khona umnyama phezu kwelizwe leGibhithe, ngitsho umnyama ophumputhekayo.
\v 22 UMozisi waseselulela isandla sakhe emazulwini; kwasekusiba khona umnyama wobumnyama\x + Hlab. 105.28.\x* elizweni lonke leGibhithe insuku ezintathu.
\v 23 Kababonananga, futhi kakusukumanga muntu endaweni yakhe okwensuku ezintathu; kodwa kubo bonke abantwana bakoIsrayeli kwakukhona ukukhanya emizini yabo\x + 8.22.\x*.
\p
\v 24 UFaro wasembiza uMozisi wathi: Hambani likhonze iN\nd kosi\nd*\x + 10.8.\x*, kuphela izimvu zenu lenkomo zenu kuzagcinwa, labantwanyana benu bazahamba lani\x + 10.10.\x*.
\v 25 Kodwa uMozisi wathi: Lawe ubonika imihlatshelo leminikelo yokutshiswa ezandleni zethu, esizayenzela iN\nd kosi\nd* uNkulunkulu wethu.
\v 26 Njalo lezifuyo zethu zizahamba kanye lathi, kakuyikusala emuva isondo; ngoba sizathatha kuzo ukukhonza iN\nd kosi\nd* uNkulunkulu wethu, ngoba kasikwazi esizakhonza ngakho iN\nd kosi\nd* size sifike khona.
\p
\v 27 Kodwa iN\nd kosi\nd* yenza lukhuni inhliziyo kaFaro\x + 10.20.\x*, njalo kafunanga ukubayekela bahambe.
\v 28 UFaro wasesithi kuye: Suka kimi, uziqaphele, ungaboni ubuso bami futhi; ngoba mhla ubona ubuso bami uzakufa.
\v 29 UMozisi wasesithi: Ukhulume ngokuqonda, kangisayikubona futhi ubuso bakho\x + Heb. 11.27.\x*.